quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  37,127,to un logon ne un ko jhutla diya. so woh ( dozakh mein ) haazir kiye jayen ge
  37,128,haan khuda ke bandgaan khaas ( mbtlaye azaab nahi ) hon ge
  37,129,aur un ka zikar ( kher ) pichlon mein ( baqi ) chore diya
  37,130,ke aِl yasin par salam
  37,131,hum naik logon ko aisa hi badla dete hain
  37,132,be shak woh hamaray momin bundon mein se they
  37,133,aur Loot bhi payghambaroon mein se they
  37,134,jab hum ne un ko aur un ke ghar walon ko sab ko ( azaab se ) nijaat di
  37,135,magar aik budiya ke peechay reh jaane walon mein thi
  37,136,phir hum ne ouron ko halaak kardiya
  37,137,aur tum din ko bhi un ( ki bustiyon ) ke paas se guzarte rehtay ho
  37,138,aur raat ko bhi. tokiya tum aqal nahi rakhtay
  37,139,aur Younis bhi payghambaroon mein se they
  37,140,jab bhaag kar bhari hui kashti mein puhanche
  37,141,is waqt quraa dala to unhon ne zuk uthai
  37,142,phir machhli ne un ko nigal liya aur woh ( qabil ) malamat ( kaam ) karne walay they
  37,143,phir agar woh ( khuda ki ) paki bayan nah karte
  37,144,to is roz taq ke log dobarah zindah kiye jayen ge isi ke pait mein rehtay
  37,145,phir hum ne un ko jab ke woh bemaar they farakh maidan mein daal diya
  37,146,aur un par kaddu ka darakht aُgaya
  37,147,aur un ko laakh ya is se ziyada ( logon ) ki taraf ( paighambar bana kar ) bheja
  37,148,to woh imaan le aeye so hum ne bhi un ko ( duniya mein ) aik waqt ( muqarrar ) taq faiday dete rahay
  37,149,un se pucho to ke bhala tumahray perwar-digaar ke liye to betiyan aur un ke liye betay
  37,150,ya hum ne firshton ko aurtain banaya aur woh ( is waqt ) mojood they
  37,151,dekho yeh apni jhoot banai hui ( baat ) kehte hain
  37,152,ke khuda ke aulaad hai kuch shak nahi ke yeh jhutay hain
  37,153,kiya is ne biton ki nisbat baityon ko pasandkiya hai ?
